\f1\b\fs32 \cf0 APP User Requirement Specification\
\pard\pardeftab708\pardirnatural

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \
The present document describes the user requirements for the APPs that will enable the user to visualize and control his house.\
\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab708\sb240\sa60\pardirnatural

\f1\b\fs32 \cf0 Installation\
\pard\pardeftab708\pardirnatural

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 The user shall select the APP from the respective store (Google, Apple, etc.) and it shall install automatically on the device after download.\
\
At first, the APP shall display the instructions for the next steps. As no house is installed, a first house installation menu will open. User must perform the following steps:\
\
Enter the name of the house\
Enter the IP address or URL of the house (default 192.168.1.31)\
Enter the port number (1470 as default)\
Now the user must enter the password on the Gateway.(ABCD...)\
Press REGISTER on APP to add the phone to the gateway\
\
